After this, you'll probably want to set up your classification system. If you are interested in ACS, use the [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/component:customizable-acs-guide Mega Cool Customizable ACS] component to establish esoteric classes w/ custom icons, and implement a custom clearance bar image if you so desire; I utilize it in all Deletions pieces (and quite a few other works of mine).

Other components you may want to use:

* [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/component:image-features Image Features] - hover, slide, blur, pixelate, fractalize your images.
* [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/component:audio-player-woed Audio Player Woed] - play sound files and control volume, tracking, downloads, etc.
* [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/component:wide-image-sizer Wide Image Sizer] - automatically scale wide images to 215px height and an appropriate width for the current screen.
